// Windows application icon. The MSVC linker embeds the first ICON resource into
// the .exe; Explorer, the taskbar, and Alt-Tab read it (and Qt uses it as the
// default window/title-bar icon). minNotes.ico is built from
// external/icons/minNotesWindows.svg by build-icon.ps1.
IDI_ICON1 ICON "minNotes.ico"
